## 2. Demo architecture

Next.js 15 App Router with `output: 'export'` + `basePath: '/demos/trucking-freight-factoring-and-banking'` + `trailingSlash: true` → static export copied to the public/demos/ deploy target. All API calls go to `https://api.michaelwegter.com/api/factoring/*` (the Flask proxy), never to localhost. NestJS runs separately (on Surface or external host), Flask proxy bridges.

Build command from `demo-src/` root:
```
corepack enable && corepack prepare pnpm@latest --activate
pnpm install
pnpm turbo run build          # builds apps/api (nest build) AND apps/web (next build)
cp -r apps/web/out/* ../../../michaelwegter.com/public/demos/trucking-freight-factoring-and-banking/
```

